Package: cambridgema
Type: Package
Title: Cambridge, MA Inspired Color Palettes for R
Version: 0.2.0
Authors@R: person("Xiaolong", "Yang",
                  email = "xiaolong.yang@example.com",
                  role = c("aut", "cre"))
Author: Xiaolong Yang [aut, cre]
Maintainer: Xiaolong Yang <xiaolong.yang@example.com>
Description: Nature-inspired color palettes based on the flora and seasons of
    Cambridge, Massachusetts. Features seasonal palettes reflecting Fresh Pond,
    Cambridge Common, and Charles River flora through the year. Includes
    discrete and continuous scales for ggplot2 plus base R helpers for easy
    integration with any plotting workflow.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
URL: https://github.com/xiaolong-y/cambridgema,
    https://xiaolong-y.github.io/cambridgema
BugReports: https://github.com/xiaolong-y/cambridgema/issues
Encoding: UTF-8
